  	  The new version of the beta is on-line!
      <br />
      Those new features have been introduced :
      <ul>
        <li> Improvement of cosine score calculation with Metgem algorithm ( https://github.com/metgem/metgem ) </li>

        <li> Availability to directly import GNPS .tsv annotation files </li>

        <li> Clone achieved project </li>

        <li> Download all molecules generated </li>

        <li> New design to select reactions and ion annotations on a project </li>

        <li>  Speed improvement to import fragmentation data </li>
